    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The taking up of the molecules of gases, dissolved substances, or liquids by the surfaces of solids and liquids with which they are in contact.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
